@startuml
title TPL Conceptual Domain - Patient Care

hide methods
hide stereotypes
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
left to right direction

class Patient
class Episode
class EpisodeOrgan
class ContactInfo
class Absence
class Diagnosis

class MedicalValueTemplate
class MedicalValueGroupTemplate
class MedicalValueGroup
class MedicalValue

Patient "1" -- "0..*" Episode
Episode "1" -- "0..*" EpisodeOrgan
Patient "1" -- "0..*" ContactInfo
Patient "1" -- "0..*" Absence
Patient "1" -- "0..*" Diagnosis

MedicalValueGroupTemplate "1" -- "0..*" MedicalValueTemplate
MedicalValueGroupTemplate "1" -- "0..*" MedicalValueGroup
Patient "1" -- "0..*" MedicalValueGroup
Patient "1" -- "0..*" MedicalValue
MedicalValueTemplate "1" -- "0..*" MedicalValue
MedicalValueGroup "1" -- "0..*" MedicalValue
Episode "1" <-- "0..*" MedicalValue : context (optional)

note bottom of MedicalValue
Medical values are context-aware:
always linked to a patient, optionally linked
to an episode (and organ context when applicable).
end note

